<lb n="1"/>śrīmannāgamahīpāla kānujō vṛṣa 
<lb n="2"/>lāṁcchanaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nārāyaṇanarēṁdrō bhūdbhā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>radvājarṣigōtrajaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē lōkaśaila 
