<lb n="8"/>gavāṁcca kṣōṇīṁ khaṁḍuprayuktā 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁ satataphalavatīṁ gōpakē kāpanāṁ 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kkē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> mōdālu 25 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> cēnu tū 20 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
